---
/*
 * Renders the README style content for the SUPERB landing page. The
 * markup here mirrors the structure of a traditional README file
 * with headings, paragraphs, and bullet points. Tailwind classes
 * provide consistent spacing and colouring to match the dark
 * aesthetic of the rest of the site.
 */
---

<div class="space-y-6">
    <!-- About section -->
    <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">About SUPERB</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
            SUPERB is an AI‑native hedge fund protocol, built fully on‑chain for the Base ecosystem. At its core is an
            autonomous agent that reallocates capital based on live signals from token launches, liquidity flows and
            on‑chain user behaviour.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4">
            Users participate by vesting <span class="text-primary font-medium">$SUPERB</span>, unlocking a continuous yield
            stream of <span class="text-primary font-medium">$SUPERBx</span> via Superfluid. This stream reflects each user’s
            proportional stake in the protocol’s on‑chain performance. No dashboards. No active trading. No
            micromanagement. Just real yield, streamed automatically.
        </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Why vaulted section -->
    <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Why We Vaulted 50% Before Launch</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
            To protect the protocol and align with our long‑term vision, 50 % of the total supply was vaulted before the
            official launch. This vault will be claimed on August 15, as originally scheduled.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4">Here’s why we did it:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-400 space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li>To protect against sniper bots and speculative manipulation</li>
            <li>To reduce volatility and avoid early concentration of tokens in a few wallets</li>
            <li>To reserve funds for the team, future airdrops, community incentives and LP provisioning</li>
            <li>To keep tokenomics fair, transparent and verifiable on‑chain from day one</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4">
            Everything is deployed, vaulted and trackable on‑chain. No surprises. No hidden wallets. No shortcuts.
        </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Core concepts section -->
    <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Core Concepts</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-400 space-y-1">
            <li><span class="text-primary font-medium">$SUPERB</span> – Governance and staking token</li>
            <li><span class="text-primary font-medium">$SUPERBx</span> – Real‑time yield stream earned by vesting</li>
            <li><span class="text-primary font-medium">AI Agent</span> – Analyses on‑chain activity and reallocates treasury capital</li>
            <li><span class="text-primary font-medium">Superfluid</span> – Streaming layer enabling continuous emissions</li>
            <li><span class="text-primary font-medium">Clanker</span> – Used to deploy the token securely on Base</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Launch section -->
    <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Launching August 15</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Built by Mutia &amp; Arian.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Focused on security, simplicity and long‑term autonomy.</p>
    </section>
</div>